comment1.text=\r\n\ Loads\ the\ next\ level\ of\ the\ game,\ or\ stops\ the\ game\ if\ the\ current\ level\r\n\ is\ the\ last\ level\ of\ the\ game.\r\n\ @param\ currentWorld\ The\ TankWorld\ object\ of\ the\ current\ level.\r\n
comment10.params=
comment10.target=void\ gameWin()
comment10.text=Displays\ a\ message\ that\ the\ player\ has\ beaten\ the\ game\ and\ stops\ the\ \r\ngame\ indefinitely.
comment11.params=
comment11.target=void\ reloadLevel()
comment11.text=Reload\ the\ level\ if\ the\ player\ tank\ has\ been\ destroyed\ but\ there\ are\ player\r\n\ \ lives\ left.\ This\ means\ the\ player\ tank\ is\ re-added\ to\ the\ world\ and\ enemy\r\n\ \ tanks\ that\ have\ not\ been\ destroyed\ are\ put\ back\ at\ their\ original\ place\r\nin\ the\ world.
comment12.params=
comment12.target=void\ gameOver()
comment12.text=Displays\ a\ message\ that\ the\ player\ has\ lost\ the\ game\ because\ it\ has\ no\ \r\nremaining\ lives\ left,\ then\ stops\ the\ game\ indefinitely.
