comment8.text=Shows\ the\ updated\ start\ screen\ display\ for\ the\ start\ of\ this\ level.\r\n\ It\ displays\ the\ current\ level\ number\ and\ the\ number\ of\ remaining\ enemy\r\ntanks\ (this\ method\ is\ also\ called\ after\ a\ level\ is\ reloaded.).
